<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Let go and let God</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 La gå og la Gud få sin herlige vei,
 la gå og la Gud få sin vei.
 Din sorg vil bli borte,
 din natt blir til dag.
 La gå og la Gud få sin vei.

[V2]
 Let go and let God
 have His wonderful way.
 Let go and let God have His way.
 Your sorrows will vanish
 your night turn to day.
 Let go and let God have His way.</lyrics>
<aka>La gå og la Gud</aka>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>